The,Zeply,Human,Translation,API,allows,developers,to,translate,content,in,real,time,using,human,translators,from,around,the,world,This,service,can,be,used,to,translate,user,generated,content,such,as,chat,messages,feedback,and,customer,support,communications,Developers,can,configure,the,service,to,automatically,translate,only,the,best,reviews,or,most,useful,comments